modules.description: This module enables text processing through Perl-compatible regular expressions, offering operations for compiling patterns with customizable flags, executing matches, and manipulating substrings via substitution or splitting. It works with strings, regular expressions, and structured match results, supporting advanced features like named capture groups, Unicode-aware matching, and file-level iteration. Use cases include parsing structured text, validating input formats, transforming codebases, and extracting data from logs or configuration files with precise control over match behavior and error handling.
